-- REQUIRED --
* Faxien
* Sinan
* Erlang R13B02-1
* Yaws
* Nitrogen
* CouchBeam

-- INSTALLING --
Get and install CouchBeam:

$ git clone git://github.com/benoitc/couchbeam.git
$ mv couchbeam couchbeam-0.1.0.0
$ cd couchbeam-0.1.0.0

Use your favorite editor to change include/couchbeam.hrl the text "boolean()" from line 23 to "true | false"

$ make
$ cd ..
$ sudo /usr/local/erlware/bin/faxien ia couchbeam-0.1.0.0

Now install Beer Enthusiasts:

$ cd beerenthusiasts
$ ./deploy

-- RUNNING --
$ beerenthusiasts
